data.description: Beautiful Colonial, in the sought after Westfields Subdivision.  This home features 3 bedrooms and 3 baths.   Gleaming hardwood floors in the foyer and on the staircase.  Open floor plan, with the kitchen overlooking the family room.  Spacious kitchen with gas cooking, showcasing an island and granite countertops.   The primary bedroom has a luxurious bath with a separate shower and soaking tub.  Large fenced rear yard backing to an open common ground with a view of the mountains.  Huge unfinished basement with rough in, plenty of space for more rooms or a home theater.  New roof 2022!  Enjoy all this community has to offer including an outdoor pool, dog park, jogging/walking paths and more!
